author: @dragonfly-7
text: Corey, I spent some time on watching your videos and you are doing just great work ! I now know to whom/what to refer to when asked by newbies for helpful resources. Awesome ! Thanks !  One comment on the keyboard shortcut section though: Almost all keyboard shortcuts of the BASH are heavily influenced by corresponding EMACS shortcuts. This might be something which could be mentioned in this context (although it might frighten VI/VIM-centric people ... ;-) )  My very personal explanation for this is that both EMACS and BASH are GNU projects ...
